        <p><lb n="1"/><g type="mangala"/><supplied reason="subaudible">.</supplied>
valkhāḥ paramabhaṭṭāraka-pādānuddhyāto mahārāja rudradāsaḥ samājñāpa<!-- 
L1 RT: transcribes mangala as om. 
--><lb break="no" n="2"/>
yati sarvvān evāsmat-santakān āyuktakān
</p>
        <p>vijñātam astu vaḥ samanu<lb break="no" n="3"/>
jānīmo <supplied reason="subaudible">’</supplied>sya vatsa-sagotra-varadeva-brāhmaṇasya brahmadatta-pratyayaṁ
<lb n="4"/>sallakīpr̥ṣṭhaka-grāmaṁ kulāgrāhāra-kkrameṇa brahmadeyaṁ śāśvata<lb break="no" n="5"/>
m ācandrā<sic>rk</sic>a-tārakā-kālīnaṁ putra-pautrānvaya-bhojyaṁ bhogāy<choice>
            <sic>eṁ</sic>
            <corr>ai</corr>
          </choice>va<lb break="no" n="6"/>
m idānīm asyāsmābhiḥ kr̥tānujñasy<choice>
            <sic>a</sic>
            <corr>o</corr>
          </choice>citayā brahmadeyikā-bhuktyā
<lb n="7"/>bhuñjataḥ samāvāsayataś ca sarvvair evāsmat-pakṣa-tat-kulyādibhiḥ sama<lb break="no" n="8"/>
numantavyam iti</p>
        <p>rudradāsa dūtakaḥ</p>
        <p>varṣe <num value="68"><g type="numeral">60</g> 8</num> Āṣāḍha śudha <num value="2">2</num></p>
